IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
   PROGRAM-ID. RECALL-FOOTER.

DATA DIVISION.
   WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      01 FOOTER-TEXT PIC X(80) VALUE "COMPILED WITH RECALL 0.1. THE SOURCE IS EMBEDDED ABOVE.".

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
   COMPONENT.
      DISPLAY FOOTER
         WITH TEXT FOOTER-TEXT
         WITH ALIGN CENTER.
      STOP SECTION.
